> Using Eligibility

# Tests: Alaska Medicaid income eligibility — covers all five 523B action paths plus IRWE and couple-type cases (benefit year 2026 unless noted). Entity prefixes: ClientData.* for client-stated inputs, DOLRecord.* for DOL-verified inputs.

## Test: ext_001 — 523B example: client $1,707.50 below A1E 2025 standard ($1,795); DOL $1,824.17 above but within 10% band — approve

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestExt001:
  result scope Eligibility.EligibilityDecision

scope TestExt001:
  definition result.client_data equals Eligibility.ClientData {
    -- gross_earned_income: $3,500
    -- federal_exclusions: $0
    -- eitc_exclusion: $0
    -- irregular_earned_income: $0
    -- student_earned_income: $0
    -- student_monthly_limit: $0
    -- non_needs_based_unearned_remainder: $20
    -- impairment_work_expenses: $0
    -- blind_work_expenses: $0
    -- self_support_exclusion: $0
    -- household_type: A1E
    -- benefit_year: 2025
  }
  definition result.d_o_l_record equals Eligibility.DOLRecord {
    -- dol_earned_income_available: true
    -- dol_quarterly_earnings: $11,200
    -- gross_earned_income: $3,733.33
    -- federal_exclusions: $0
    -- eitc_exclusion: $0
    -- irregular_earned_income: $0
    -- student_earned_income: $0
    -- student_monthly_limit: $0
    -- non_needs_based_unearned_remainder: $20
    -- impairment_work_expenses: $0
    -- blind_work_expenses: $0
    -- self_support_exclusion: $0
  }
  assertion (result.eligible = Approve)
  assertion (result.reasons = [])
```

